                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-278-off1562 t18320906-278-cd1563"></join>, 1 pair of stays, value 3s., and 3 hand<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183209060122"></xptr>kerchiefs, value 5s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-278-victim2300" type="victimName">
